            html_content: '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang="zh-CN">\n<head>\n<meta charset="UTF-8">\n<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">\n<title>TechBlog</title>\n<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">\n</head>\n<body>\n<nav class="nav"><a href="#" class="logo">TechBlog</a><div class="nav-links"><a href="#">首页</a><a href="#">文章</a><a href="#">关于</a></div></nav>\n<main class="container">\n<article class="post-card"><div class="post-cover" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#8b5cf6)"></div><div class="post-body"><h2>如何使用 Autoconfig 部署你的第一个项目</h2><p>只需上传 ZIP 文件，即可秒变公网网站。本文将介绍从零开始的完整部署流程。</p><div class="post-meta"><span>2026-04-01</span><span>阅读 5 分钟</span></div></div></article>\n<article class="post-card"><div class="post-cover" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f59e0b,#ef4444)"></div><div class="post-body"><h2>JavaScript 异步编程完全指南</h2><p>从回调函数到 async/await，深入理解 JavaScript 异步编程的前世今生。</p><div class="post-meta"><span>2026-03-28</span><span>阅读 10 分钟</span></div></div></article>\n</main>\n<footer class="footer">© 2026 TechBlog · Powered by Autoconfig</footer>\n</body>\n</html>',
            css_content: '*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}\nbody{background:#0f172a;color:#e2e8f0;font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;line-height:1.6}\n.nav{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;max-width:768px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px}\n.logo{font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:800;color:#818cf8;text-decoration:none}\n.nav-links{display:flex;gap:20px}\n.nav-links a{color:#94a3b8;text-decoration:none;font-size:.9rem;transition:color .3s}\n.nav-links a:hover{color:#e2e8f0}\n.container{max-width:768px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px}\n.post-card{background:#1e293b;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:24px;transition:transform .3s}\n.post-card:hover{transform:translateY(-4px)}\n.post-cover{height:180px}\n.post-body{padding:24px}\n.post-body h2{font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:12px}\n.post-body p{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:16px}\n.post-meta{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:.8rem;color:#64748b}\n.footer{text-align:center;padding:40px;color:#475569;font-size:.85rem}',
